nodes.text: Star Wars: The Clone Wars Magazine 19
Star Wars: The Clone Wars Magazine 19 is the nineteenth issue of the Star Wars: The Clone Wars Magazine. It was released on August 7, 2013.

The latest series of the Star Wars: The Clone Wars may be over, but the adventures continue in the new issue of the magazine! After the Jedi battle an army of escaped bounty hunters in the first of two terrific comic tales, we check out the galaxy's littlest heroes when Ahsoka shows a new batch of Younglings the path of the Jedi! Then, we take a dive under the waters of Mon Calamari, where Obi-Wan comes face-to-face with the breakout star of A New Hope - that's right, the dianoga! It's got its eye on you!
